.food52.com/cx1wLwN4J6VSfcBIi85Wp0Wri0I=/1536x1536/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/vGG5FEYmpVryLNVwdWzCb8fLP1Q=/375x375/filters:format(webp)/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg, https://images.food52.com/nS8rLes7QEh-LtdQ5EnnvHR_CU4=/750x750/filters:format(webp)/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/9b4wCNAcof0SX6zPynOiveFfqcY=/375x375/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg, https://images.food52.com/DlJqDFcilW1EbetvADy1XXuAY7M=/750x750/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"964\" height=\"964\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/9b4wCNAcof0SX6zPynOiveFfqcY=/375x375/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg, https://images.food52.com/DlJqDFcilW1EbetvADy1XXuAY7M=/750x750/f3d41cb9-21ea-45ea-8410-b76b82886c43--2021-1001_blomus_modern-steel-fireplace-accessories_1x1_james-ransom-186.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cfigcaption\u003e\n\n          \u003cspan\u003ePhoto by James Ransom\u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \u003ch2\u003eTreat Yourself to a Solo Spa Celebration\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eNot every birthday calls for a big bash. Sometimes, the best gift is a little self-care. Swap out the typical workday for a 9-to-5 spa day and emerge refreshed. After all, it’s hard to remember the wind chill factor when you’re sweating in a sauna.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n\n  \n\n              \u003ch2\u003eTake a Birthday Stroll with a Twist\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003ePick your favorite neighborhood and turn your birthday into a casual bar hop or coffee crawl. With a drink in hand and your favorite people by your side, even a cold February day can feel warm and lively.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eWinter birthdays might not come with sunshine and rooftop parties, but that doesn’t mean they can’t be just as fun. However you choose to celebrate, make sure it feels right for you—because at the end of the day, your birthday should be exactly what you want it to be.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/Z84pezdtDtWOTCbRzTLcrVSKRxQ=/778x778/filters:format(webp)/e7e47bb4-e918-4774-bcae-0dc7f9fa57